#### 方法一：一次遍历

**思路与算法**

我们可以对字符串 $s$ 进行一次遍历。当遍历到位置 $i$ 时，计算 $s[i]$ 与 $s[i+1]$ 的 $\text{ASCII}$ 码差值的绝对值，并累加入答案即可。

注意最后一个字符无需进行遍历。

**代码**

```C++ [sol1-C++]
class Solution {
public:
    int scoreOfString(string s) {
        int n = s.size();
        int score = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i + 1 < n; ++i) {
            score += abs(s[i] - s[i + 1]);
        }
        return score;
    }
};
```

```Python [sol1-Python3]
class Solution:
    def scoreOfString(self, s: str) -> int:
        n = len(s)
        score = 0
        for i in range(n - 1):
            score += abs(ord(s[i]) - ord(s[i + 1]))
        return score
```

```Go [sol1-Go]
func scoreOfString(s string) int {
    n, score := len(s), 0
    for i := 0; i + 1 < n; i++ {
        i1, i2 := int(s[i]), int(s[i + 1])
        if i1 - i2 < 0 {
            score += i2 - i1
        } else {
            score += i1 - i2
        }
    }
    return score
}
```

```C [sol1-C]
int scoreOfString(char* s) {
    int n = strlen(s);
    int score = 0;
    for (int i = 0; i + 1 < n; ++i) {
        score += abs(s[i] - s[i + 1]);
    }
    return score;
}
```

```Java [sol1-Java]
class Solution {
    public int scoreOfString(String s) {
        int score = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < s.length() - 1; i++) {
            score += Math.abs(s.charAt(i) - s.charAt(i + 1));
        }
        return score;
    }
}
```

